text: "Violently Happy" is a 1994 song by Icelandic singer Björk and is the fifth single from her debut studio album Debut. It went to number 13 in the United Kingdom, number 15 in Scotland, number 31 in France, number 94 in Australia and number 100 in Germany. ==Track listings== ==References== Category:1994 songs Category:Björk songs
title: Violently Happy
